Header.title: Welcome to 750 YP
Header.paragraph: Connecting you with other young professionals in the DFW region.

About.paragraph: 750 YP is a new program of the Lewisville Area Chamber of Commerce that aims to gather you talent while developing the next generation fo leaders. This group will offer a wealth of opportunities for young professionals to network, give back to the community, and grow both personally and professionally. Brunches take place every month of on the 2nd Tuesday of the month and mixers are held on the 4th Thursday.
